data.description:
Welcome to your Modern Craftsman Oasis! This beautifully renovated home in the heart of North Park will leave you in Awe! No expense spared with Gorgeous French Oak flooring throughout an entertainers kitchen, in-suite laundry, and European Hotel-Style Luxurious Bathrooms! The master bathroom's shower alone has 12 (yes 12) nozzles and heads!! This Boho Gem boasts White & Gold Countertops, top-of-the-line smart appliances, and is just blocks from 30th Street, University Ave, and Balboa Park! Private parking as well as street parking available and fenced front & back yards. Enjoy your peace coming home to this Gem!

One year lease preferred, Owners pay trash and sewage. Renter must carry renters insurance and have good credit and rental history! Additional terms and conditions can be negotiated
